    <narrativeNotes>Magic Baby McBibby was born to a simple medieval peasant impacted by a quantum-entanglement phenomenon, imbuing her fetus-self with powerful psycasting potential. At the end of her mortal life, Magic Baby sought immortality and attempted to hijack an Archoseed's body. Though briefly successful, the form destabilised and could only reform in the backrooms, where Magic Baby was forced to adapt to the futuristic enviroments and horros.</narrativeNotes>
